title: Robbie Rivera LIVE at W Hotel Miami FL (WMC) - 25.03.2011
description: Ultra Music Festival is an annual outdoor electronic music festival that occurs in March in the city of Miami usually during the annual Winter Music Conference. It was a 1-day festival from 1999-2006, a 2-day festival from 2007-2010, and has been announced as a 3-day festival in 2011. It is one of the highest grossing music festivals in the world.
